ARTICLE.TITLE: Fatal car blast in downtown Kitchener possibly caused by IED, police say-CBC
ARTICLE.TEXT:
One person is dead after a car explosion in front of the courthouse in downtown Kitchener Friday morning. Police say it appears the blast was from an improvised explosive device.
